<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI产品蝗虫团 - 群聊日报</title>
    <link href="https://lf3-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://lf6-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-100-M/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #FF7E33;
            --secondary: #FFB347;
            --accent: #FFD166;
            --background: #FFF5EB;
            --text: #333333;
            --card-bg: #FFFFFF;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 1rem;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .bento-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            grid-auto-rows: minmax(150px, auto);
            gap: 20px;
            grid-template-areas:
                "summary summary"
                "hot-topics active-users"
                "tech-share tech-share"
                "quotes resources"
                "word-cloud word-cloud";
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .bento-grid {
                grid-template-areas:
                    "summary"
                    "hot-topics"
                    "active-users"
                    "tech-share"
                    "quotes"
                    "resources"
                    "word-cloud";
            }
        }

        .card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
        }

        .summary-card {
            grid-area: summary;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .summary-card::before {
            display: none;
        }

        .hot-topics-card {
            grid-area: hot-topics;
        }

        .active-users-card {
            grid-area: active-users;
        }

        .tech-share-card {
            grid-area: tech-share;
        }

        .quotes-card {
            grid-area: quotes;
        }

        .resources-card {
            grid-area: resources;
        }

        .word-cloud-card {
            grid-area: word-cloud;
            min-height: 300px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: inherit;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .user-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .user-badge .count {
            margin-left: 0.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .word-cloud {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .word-cloud span {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .word-size-1 { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .word-size-2 { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .word-size-3 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .word-size-4 { font-size: 1.75rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .word-size-5 { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--primary); }

        .icon {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0.1;
            font-size: 5rem;
            right: 1rem;
            bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .link {
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bento-grid">
        <div class="card summary-card">
            <h1>AI产品蝗虫团 · 群聊日报</h1>
            <p>2025年6月17日 · 00:28 - 13:38</p>
            <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                <div>
                    <h3>消息总数</h3>
                    <p class="text-2xl font-bold">500</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>活跃用户</h3>
                    <p class="text-2xl font-bold">45</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>有效消息</h3>
                    <p class="text-2xl font-bold">451</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>热点话题</h3>
                    <p class="text-2xl font-bold">8</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <i class="icon fas fa-robot"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="card hot-topics-card">
            <h2>今日热点</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap">
                <span class="tag">豆包1.6</span>
                <span class="tag">Gemini更新</span>
                <span class="tag">字节AI投入</span>
                <span class="tag">腾讯AI战略</span>
                <span class="tag">AI编程工具</span>
                <span class="tag">学习机AI</span>
                <span class="tag">播客生成</span>
                <span class="tag">Cursor使用</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <h3>热门讨论</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                    <li>豆包1.6功能强大，KOL集体推广</li>
                    <li>Gemini即将发布2.5-Flash-Lite版本</li>
                    <li>字节跳动去年AI投入200亿美元</li>
                    <li>腾讯围绕微信构建AI生态</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <i class="icon fas fa-fire"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="card active-users-card">
            <h2>活跃之星</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap">
                <span class="user-badge">神的孩子在跳舞 <span class="count">102</span></span>
                <span class="user-badge">Ronin_Chang <span class="count">60</span></span>
                <span class="user-badge">不倒翁先生 <span class="count">49</span></span>
                <span class="user-badge">刘博 <span class="count">27</span></span>
                <span class="user-badge"> <span class="count">26</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <h3>精彩发言</h3>
                <p>"豆包的商单集体爆发了，KOL全部都在推豆包1.6" - 神的孩子在跳舞</p>
                <p class="mt-2">"架构师订死，不写代码，只聊逻辑" - 不倒翁先生</p>
            </div>
            <i class="icon fas fa-star"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="card tech-share-card">
            <h2>技术分享</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div>
                    <h3>AI编程工具</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                        <li>Cursor vs Augment对比讨论</li>
                        <li>多Agent协作编程方法论</li>
                        <li>Gemini代码格式化技巧</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>资源推荐</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                        <li>Liquid Glass React组件</li>
                        <li>Markdown转微信公众号工具</li>
                        <li>Interactive Feedback MCP</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <i class="icon fas fa-code"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="card quotes-card">
            <h2>精彩引用</h2>
            <blockquote class="italic border-l-4 border-orange-300 pl-4 py-2">
                "真正的行业智慧不在于知道一切，而在于知道什么最重要。好的引路人不是倾倒知识，而是点亮路径。"
            </blockquote>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">- Eliot分享的提示词框架</p>

            <blockquote class="italic border-l-4 border-orange-300 pl-4 py-2 mt-4">
                "可以想象成一个编程团队，你要一个架构师agent，一个整理文档的agent，一个写代码的agent，一个查资料的agent。直接让一个agent完成，质量怎么可能好。"
            </blockquote>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">- 不倒翁先生</p>
            <i class="icon fas fa-quote-right"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="card resources-card">
            <h2>重要资源</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li><a href="https://github.com/rdev/liquid-glass-react" class="link">Liquid Glass React组件</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://github.com/caol64/wenyan-mcp" class="link">Markdown转微信公众号工具</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://github.com/poliva/interactive-feedback-mcp" class="link">Interactive Feedback MCP</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://turso.tech/blog/working-on-databases-from-prison" class="link">监狱中开发数据库的故事</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.bestblogs.dev/podcast/f371386" class="link">AI播客分享</a></li>
            </ul>
            <i class="icon fas fa-link"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="card word-cloud-card">
            <h2>话题词云</h2>
            <div class="word-cloud">
                <span class="word-size-5">豆包</span>
                <span class="word-size-4">Gemini</span>
                <span class="word-size-4">AI</span>
                <span class="word-size-3">编程</span>
                <span class="word-size-3">字节</span>
                <span class="word-size-3">腾讯</span>
                <span class="word-size-2">模型</span>
                <span class="word-size-2">Agent</span>
                <span class="word-size-2">Cursor</span>
                <span class="word-size-2">架构</span>
                <span class="word-size-1">播客</span>
                <span class="word-size-1">学习机</span>
                <span class="word-size-1">投资</span>
                <span class="word-size-1">代码</span>
                <span class="word-size-1">提示词</span>
            </div>
            <i class="icon fas fa-cloud"></i>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 简单的词云效果
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const words = document.querySelectorAll('.word-cloud span');
            words.forEach(word => {
                const rotation = Math.floor(Math.random() * 30) - 15;
                word.style.transform = `rotate(${rotation}deg)`;
                word.style.display = 'inline-block';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
